| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4961 — Mass File Rename (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 56cf67de-b3bc-5f9e-b122-15e770493329"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
